&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; journey is the best way to weave through the notch caves, explore quiet lagoons, and get the closest access to the magnificent limestone islands that large boats cannot reach. This experience not only brings absolute relaxation amid the tranquil nature of Lan Ha Bay but is also an effective &quot;healing&quot; therapy for the soul and physical training.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Why is the Lan Ha Bay kayak tour an experience not to be missed?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay, located to the south of Ha Long Bay and surrounding the Cat Ba archipelago, is known as a &quot;forgotten paradise&quot; with pristine beauty and a far more peaceful atmosphere than its famous neighbor. To fully appreciate this beauty, taking part in a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; is the top choice for nature lovers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;In particular, the Lan Ha Bay area has hundreds of small unnamed beaches. Only with a true &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; itinerary do you get the chance to &quot;have to yourself&quot; a small private beach, relaxing and breathing in the sea air without being disturbed by engine noise or dust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/0000/1/2025/12/30/lan-ha-bay-kayak-tour-1.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The ideal time to take a Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Choosing the departure time plays a decisive role in the success of the trip. A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; will be most perfect when the weather is favorable, the sea is calm, and the sky is clear and blue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;From March to May (Spring): This is when the weather gradually warms up, the sky is clear, and there is little rain. This is the most ideal period for kayaking because you are neither too hot under the sun nor too cold from the sea breeze.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;From September to November (Autumn): After the sweltering, stormy summer months, autumn brings cool air and a bay surface as smooth as a mirror. A Lan Ha Bay kayak tour at this time will help you capture extremely impressive sunset photos over the sea.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Summer note (June - August): Although it is the peak tourist season, storms are also frequent. If you choose a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; at this time, you need to closely monitor the weather forecast to avoid sudden thunderstorms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/0000/1/2025/12/30/lan-ha-bay-kayak-tour-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The most beautiful spots on a Lan Ha Bay kayak tour journey&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay possesses an extremely diverse system of caves and lagoons. Below are the stops that no professional &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; should miss:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Bright Cave and Dark Cave (Dark and Bright Caves)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;This is the area bordering Lan Ha Bay and Ha Long Bay, famous for its mysterious beauty. When taking a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; here, you will paddle through a rock cave about 100m long to enter a lagoon completely enclosed by towering cliffs. The space inside is utterly silent, with only the sound of water dripping from the stalactites, giving the feeling of being lost in another world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The Ao Ech (Frog Pond) area&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;True to its name, this is a place with unique natural scenery featuring oddly shaped limestone blocks. The water surface at Ao Ech is very calm, extremely suitable for first-time &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; participants. You can leisurely paddle, watching the coral reefs faintly visible beneath the clear water.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Ba Trai Dao Beach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;This area consists of three small islands that look like three heavenly peaches. It is an ideal resting stop on a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; itinerary. After paddling until exhausted, you can plunge into the cool water or lie lazily on the fine white sand to enjoy the sunshine.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Cua Van and Cai Beo fishing villages&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;If you want to learn about local culture, steer your boat toward the ancient fishing villages. A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; through the floating houses will help you observe the daily life of the fishermen, how they raise fish in cages, and the hospitality of the seaside people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;color:#e74c3c;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt;In addition, discover more high-quality travel experiences at&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://vietnamtoure.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;color:#e74c3c;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt; virenaretreat.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/0000/1/2025/12/30/lan-ha-bay-kayak-tour-3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; height=&quot;605&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;How to choose a reputable Lan Ha Bay kayak tour operator?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;There are currently many companies offering this service, but to have a safe and rewarding trip, you need to consider carefully. A quality &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; should ensure the following factors:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Safety equipment: The kayak must be sturdy, the paddle light, and especially there must always be standard-quality life jackets for tourists.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Experienced guides: A guide who knows the terrain well will help you find the most beautiful routes and handle unexpected situations at sea. On a Lan Ha Bay kayak tour, the guide is also the person who tells you interesting stories about the bay&#039;s history and geology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Commitment to environmental protection: Prioritize operators that emphasize sustainable tourism and leave no waste behind while running the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;. This aligns with the spirit of &quot;healing&quot; and respecting nature.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Flexible itinerary: Small, personalized tours often provide better emotions than mass tours with too many people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/0000/1/2025/12/30/lan-ha-bay-kayak-tour-6.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Items to prepare for a Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;To fully enjoy the fun, preparing personal items is very important. When going on a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Lan Ha Bay kayak tour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;, make sure you bring:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
